Properties.Name: Get Parent Project GUID via SQL

Properties.Value:
SELECT Guid
FROM _com_blueboxmoon_ProjectManagement_Project
WHERE Id = (SELECT EntityId AS ProjectGUID
FROM AttributeValue
WHERE AttributeId = '16217' AND Value = '{{ Workflow | Attribute:'ReservationId' }}')

Properties.Name: Set Children ages from resource options (Attribute Id 5889)

Properties.Value:
SELECT TOP 1
	[Value]
FROM [AttributeValue]
Where [Value] <> '' AND AttributeId = '5889' AND EntityId = '{{ Workflow | Attribute:'ResourceId' }}'
